{"tid":1503709,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疑FB發反修例訊息 傳再多一名國泰機師遭解僱","createTime":"2019-08-25T05:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T07:31:48.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"736192a4395949bbe61e6fdf0bc446d76f776adb","tid":1503709,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190825/_2019082512232978956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190825%2F_2019082512232978956.jpg&h=fa5b02d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有消息指，再有一名國泰機師疑因在社交媒體發放涉及反對修訂《逃犯條例》的內容被公司解僱。<br />\n<br />\n之前有指，一位國泰機師早前於美國駕駛飛機回港時，因需經過內地空域而被內地禁止，最終由另一位同事代駕。最新消息傳出，這名機師已離職。根據航線，美國和歐洲大部分的回程航班，都需飛越內地空域。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，有關的機師與港龍空勤人員協會主席施安娜情況相似，被管理層召見時，同場展示多幅facebook截圖，待對方確認屬於其帳戶後便即時解僱。<br />\n<br />\n中國民航局早前對國泰航空發出重大航空安全風險警示，提出停止有參與衝擊活動航空人員的內地航班職務等要求。事發至今連同這宗，國泰共有2名高級管理層、5名機師，和施安娜先後離職或被解僱。"},{"pid":"399e7dc89d6627d5163ddc27e86ab7a6cddbe392","tid":1503709,"uid":198008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2146221e05c656a7643950673f404076c0bf2bbf","tid":1503709,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T06:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xq9vLGo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXq9vLGo.jpg&h=8e276ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wdS5zzL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwdS5zzL.jpg&h=fc5af98f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c03c638fcda65b85a8e4af4956c8e7843c370b5e","tid":1503709,"uid":290106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22d2ddcba47271213e577a27707b5cb6fd5eacf4","tid":1503709,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor